summary: This save file is for those who need the Master Architect Achievement unlocked. I know I had some problems with bugs and glitches where the achievement didn\'t unlock for me, so I made this save file so you may skip those problems.
descriptionHtml:
Just download the file, extract it, and place in your save location. Load the file and complete the Enchanting Tower at Windstad Manor. You\'ll have plently of materials to finish the tower. The other two Hearthfire houses are already complete. Just complete the Enchanting Tower at Windstad manor and you\'re all set.

If you have any questions, feel free to post.

NOTE:

Hearthfire DLC and Dawnguard DLC is needed for this file. Sorry for the inconvenience.
author: SteelCityMB
